sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant SupervisorAI
    participant PlannerAI
    participant ContextManager
    participant AgentRegistry
    participant ExecutionPolicies
    participant TaskGraphEngine
    participant Agent

    User->>SupervisorAI: Submit High-Level Objective
    SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Validate Objective
    SupervisorAI->>PlannerAI: Request Plan (Objective)
    PlannerAI->>PlannerAI: Decompose Objective into Tasks
    PlannerAI->>TaskGraphEngine: Build DAG (Tasks, Dependencies)
    TaskGraphEngine-->>PlannerAI: DAG
    PlannerAI-->>SupervisorAI: Execution Plan (DAG)
    SupervisorAI->>ContextManager: Store Initial Context (Plan, Objective)
    SupervisorAI->>AgentRegistry: Discover Available Agents
    AgentRegistry-->>SupervisorAI: List of Agents
    SupervisorAI->>ExecutionPolicies: Select Execution Policy
    ExecutionPolicies-->>SupervisorAI: Selected Policy
    SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Assign Agents to Tasks (based on Policy, Capabilities)

    loop For each Task in DAG (Topological Order)
        SupervisorAI->>ContextManager: Get Task Context
        ContextManager-->>SupervisorAI: Task Context
        SupervisorAI->>Agent: Execute Task (Task, Context, Policy)
        Agent->>Agent: Perform Work
        Agent->>ContextManager: Update Task Context
        ContextManager-->>Agent: Confirmation
        Agent-->>SupervisorAI: Task Result (Success/Failure)
        SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Monitor Task Status
        alt If Task Fails
            SupervisorAI->>PlannerAI: Request Re-plan (Failed Task, Current State)
            PlannerAI-->>SupervisorAI: New/Updated Plan
            SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Adjust Execution
        end
    end

    SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Merge Outputs
    SupervisorAI->>ContextManager: Store Final Result & Audit Trail
    ContextManager-->>SupervisorAI: Confirmation
    SupervisorAI-->>User: Final Result & Audit Report
